<item>
            <title>[HBASE-7050] Document locking of HRegion</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-7050</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Would be good to have some documentation on the locking in HRegion.  In particular, the updateLock and the row locks.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;With the optimizations that have been made, e.g. &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-5541&quot; title=&quot;Avoid holding the rowlock during HLog sync in HRegion.mutateRowWithLocks&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;HBASE-5541&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;HBASE-5541&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; this isn&apos;t straightforward.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;When do these locks need to be held?  What structures do they protect access to?  Why does the updateLock not need to be held during rollback?  Those sorts of questions.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I&apos;ve started do to some of this, but haven&apos;t fully fleshed it out.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
